{"tid":2074621,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"仲量聯行：中環甲級寫字樓空置率升至12年新高","createTime":"2020-06-22T08:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T08:47:28.000Z","uid":60281,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"964a8dfb2dc46c8a718f69ef69ffff6049da0da5","tid":2074621,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T08:47:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n物業顧問仲量聯行指出，5月中環甲級寫字樓空置率5%，較4月上升0.4個百分點，是08年金融海嘯後最高，導致租金按月下跌2.7%，跌至平均每平方呎102.4元，跌幅較4月收窄1.8個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，5月整體甲級寫字樓空置率7.4%，上升0.2個百分點，租金按月下跌2.2%。尖沙咀及九龍東寫字樓空置率分別升至6.5%及13.7%，是各區中最高。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533423-20200622.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533423-20200622.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F5LurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=0d0b2f63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533423-20200622.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7ee2aa40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533423-20200622.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}